      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of the final analog M-car. Under the hood, the S54 inline-six screams to an 8,000 RPM redline, featuring independent throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double VANOS system. Power is routed through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential. The chassis remains factory-stiff with no subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry is strictly OEM. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon, the paint depth and interior bolsters are flawless. This is a turn-key masterpiece for the purist seeking mechanical perfection.",
